387
00:29:13,847 --> 00:29:15,360
Then you made Tankhun think that

388
00:29:15,389 --> 00:29:16,989
I was the one who found the body, right?

389
00:29:21,330 --> 00:29:22,330
That’s right!

390
00:29:24,280 --> 00:29:25,469
So he will know

391
00:29:26,800 --> 00:29:28,800
