392
00:29:30,600 --> 00:29:32,741
But he just happened to jump in beforehand!

393
00:29:33,400 --> 00:29:35,527
So he became your witness!

394
00:29:39,900 --> 00:29:40,640
Tan!

395
00:29:40,683 --> 00:29:42,243
Because you’re just the second in class

396
00:29:43,927 --> 00:29:45,930
