397
00:29:47,310 --> 00:29:48,501
How did you get here?

398
00:29:53,080 --> 00:29:54,312
Because I’m the number one.

399
00:30:24,960 --> 00:30:25,960
Hey.

400
00:30:26,510 --> 00:30:27,570
I’m safe.

401
00:30:27,990 --> 00:30:30,138
Your brother went inside to check on Pleng.

402
00:30:30,181 --> 00:30:31,190
By the way,

403
00:30:31,221 --> 00:30:33,190
