404
00:30:40,610 --> 00:30:41,701
(Are you okay?)

405
00:30:42,070 --> 00:30:43,665
I don’t get hurt that easily.

406
00:30:43,709 --> 00:30:45,214
Otherwise, I wouldn’t dare come here.

407
00:30:54,190 --> 00:30:55,832
What’s this joke?

408
00:30:58,700 --> 00:31:00,420
It’s right what you’re thinking, Inspector.

409
00:31:01,000 --> 00:31:02,734
Tankhun and I are inseparable.

410
00:31:03,500 --> 00:31:04,967
If we were to separate,

411
00:31:05,790 --> 00:31:08,130
