415
00:31:19,610 --> 00:31:21,912
It could have ended with your mom!

416
00:31:22,860 --> 00:31:24,552
Your mom is a murderer.

417
00:31:25,389 --> 00:31:27,003
I dug and found

418
00:31:27,032 --> 00:31:29,000
that your mom killed Thunphob

419
00:31:29,580 --> 00:31:32,232
and covered her own son’s memory.

420
00:31:32,850 --> 00:31:34,167
That’s because her son knew

421
00:31:34,218 --> 00:31:35,578
that she had an affair.

422
00:31:37,381 --> 00:31:38,669
And your younger brother,

423
00:31:39,390 --> 00:31:42,225
who had to help revive his memory,

424
00:31:42,870 --> 00:31:44,603
unluckily got dragged into it.

425
00:31:45,105 --> 00:31:46,105
Then Tanu

426
00:31:46,150 --> 00:31:47,694
was the one who ruined your plan.

427
00:31:48,570 --> 00:31:51,680
Tanu’s appearance changed the assumptions.

428
00:31:52,152 --> 00:31:53,614
So you tried to do everything

429
00:31:53,643 --> 00:31:55,250
to find the link between Tanu

430
00:31:55,287 --> 00:31:56,509
and Pleng’s family.

431
00:31:57,040 --> 00:31:58,829
The fishing line

432
00:31:58,858 --> 00:32:01,367
was some false evidence that you made up.

433
00:32:01,800 --> 00:32:02,800
Yeah.

434
00:32:04,070 --> 00:32:07,781
But you came up with some damn theory

435
00:32:07,810 --> 00:32:09,621
