to lure out the suspect.

439
00:32:17,010 --> 00:32:19,796
F*ck, I was right beside you!

440
00:32:21,680 --> 00:32:22,680
So what?

441
00:32:23,060 --> 00:32:24,356
Sooner or later,

442
00:32:24,400 --> 00:32:25,880
I still figure out what you’re up to.

443
00:32:26,330 --> 00:32:28,189
Even if you killed everyone here,

444
00:32:28,218 --> 00:32:29,541
