445
00:32:29,563 --> 00:32:30,778
Who would ever believe you?

446
00:32:32,500 --> 00:32:33,985
Then you can be the first to die.

447
00:32:35,160 --> 00:32:36,160
Tan!

448
00:32:40,100 --> 00:32:41,105
That’s not it!

449
00:32:41,800 --> 00:32:43,316
Petchkla never cheated

450
00:32:43,880 --> 00:32:45,694
and I never had an affair.

451
00:32:46,550 --> 00:32:48,283
I didn’t kill Thunphob!

452
00:32:49,600 --> 00:32:50,523
You!

453
00:32:50,545 --> 00:32:52,520
You’re still lying even now.

454
00:32:55,910 --> 00:32:56,450
Tan!

455
00:32:56,480 --> 00:32:57,592
Pleng! Go!

456
00:32:57,621 --> 00:32:58,621
Get off me!

457
00:33:11,978 --> 00:33:12,661
Urgh!

458
00:33:12,950 --> 00:33:14,290
Stop it!

459
00:33:14,312 --> 00:33:15,498
Let go of me!

460
00:33:15,541 --> 00:33:16,541
Let go!

461
00:33:16,600 --> 00:33:17,600
Let go of me!

462
00:33:19,990 --> 00:33:21,585
Mrs. Khitakan didn’t do it.

463
00:33:23,590 --> 00:33:24,720
I did it!

464
00:33:25,910 --> 00:33:27,054
Why did you do it?

465
00:33:27,770 --> 00:33:28,792
Because that person

466
00:33:30,630 --> 00:33:32,683
was going to tell everyone that Botpleng’s dead.

467
00:33:39,480 --> 00:33:41,127
What the hell are you saying?

468
00:33:41,170 --> 00:33:43,330
Botpleng is sitting right here.

469
00:33:43,360 --> 00:33:44,945
Like shit, he’s dead!

470
00:33:44,974 --> 00:33:46,058
Shut up!

471
00:33:46,087 --> 00:33:47,694
I said I did it!

472
00:33:48,300 --> 00:33:49,323
Let go of me!

473
00:33:53,600 --> 00:33:54,600
Tontharn.

474
00:33:56,640 --> 00:33:57,640
Dad is sorry.

475
00:34:05,730 --> 00:34:07,730
(My name is Botpleng Thayadon)

476
00:34:08,632 --> 00:34:10,630
(The only child of my parents.)

477
00:34:11,800 --> 00:34:13,163
How is it going, Tanu?

478
00:34:14,940 --> 00:34:16,327
Hello, Mrs. Kan.

479
00:34:16,363 --> 00:34:17,396
Hello, Mr. Petch.

480
00:34:25,738 --> 00:34:27,818
BOTPLENG THAYADON.

481
00:34:31,820 --> 00:34:33,752
His handwriting is just like Botpleng’s.

482
00:34:33,781 --> 00:34:35,985
They were probably brothers in the previous life.

483
00:34:37,830 --> 00:34:39,425
Thank you so much, Mrs. Kan,

484
00:34:39,469 --> 00:34:41,585
