485
00:34:43,790 --> 00:34:44,790
Hey.

486
00:34:44,950 --> 00:34:46,138
Say thank you to Mrs. Kan.

487
00:34:46,174 --> 00:34:47,658
TONTHARN THIWFON.

488
00:34:47,687 --> 00:34:49,447
Thank you, Mrs. Kan.

489
00:34:50,980 --> 00:34:53,272
