490
00:34:57,990 --> 00:34:59,054
Thank you, Mom.

491
00:35:08,810 --> 00:35:11,432
Be my brother, Tontharn.

492
00:35:12,840 --> 00:35:13,840
(No.)

493
00:35:16,040 --> 00:35:17,454
(I’m not Botpleng.)

494
00:35:19,018 --> 00:35:21,020
(I am Tontharn Thiwfon.)

495
00:35:22,780 --> 00:35:24,130
(Tanu’s son.)

496
00:35:35,290 --> 00:35:36,560
You’re back already, Mom?

497
00:35:38,680 --> 00:35:40,763
I’m cooking some rice.

498
00:35:40,800 --> 00:35:41,970
Please wait a bit.

499
00:35:46,021 --> 00:35:47,214
Ow!

500
00:35:48,560 --> 00:35:49,440
I knew what you did.

501
00:35:49,483 --> 00:35:51,365
You went to play with the boy from that family again, right?

502
00:35:51,389 --> 00:35:53,029
You want to become their son so bad, huh?

503
00:35:53,054 --> 00:35:53,760
I’m sorry.

504
00:35:53,796 --> 00:35:55,328
You want to become their son so bad, huh?

505
00:35:55,352 --> 00:35:57,090
It hurts, Mom!

506
00:35:57,120 --> 00:35:58,000
- I’m sorry.
- Get out of my house!

507
00:35:58,036 --> 00:35:59,381
I love you, Mom.

508
00:35:59,418 --> 00:36:00,640
You bastard of a son!

509
00:36:00,974 --> 00:36:02,101
You horrible son!

510
00:36:02,123 --> 00:36:03,352
Get out!

511
00:36:07,670 --> 00:36:09,352
You got hit by your mom again?

512
00:36:09,752 --> 00:36:11,192
I told you to stand up for yourself.

513
00:36:13,200 --> 00:36:15,110
But she’s my mom, Mr. Pleng.

514
00:36:17,461 --> 00:36:19,549
I told you to call me brother.

515
00:36:23,320 --> 00:36:25,512
But my mom doesn’t want me to get close to you.

516
00:36:26,580 --> 00:36:28,909
To me, you’re my younger brother.

517
00:36:29,396 --> 00:36:31,400
To Mom, you’re a son.

518
00:36:31,960 --> 00:36:33,481
Don’t you want to be my younger brother

519
00:36:33,505 --> 00:36:34,778
and Mom’s son?

520
00:36:37,850 --> 00:36:38,850
I do.

521
00:36:39,930 --> 00:36:41,461
I want to become Mom Kan’s son

522
00:36:42,350 --> 00:36:44,030
and I want to become your younger brother.

523
00:36:46,430 --> 00:36:47,767
Then trust in me.

524
00:36:48,360 --> 00:36:50,705
I’ll make you my younger brother.

525
00:36:52,545 --> 00:36:53,607
Botpleng!

526
00:36:54,600 --> 00:36:56,116
Botpleng! Tontharn!

527
00:36:56,440 --> 00:36:57,840
Where are you?

528
00:36:58,520 --> 00:36:59,658
Botpleng!

529
00:37:08,334 --> 00:37:09,334
Pleng!

530
00:37:10,790 --> 00:37:11,796
Pleng!

531
00:37:11,832 --> 00:37:12,832
Pleng!

532
00:37:13,790 --> 00:37:14,790
Pleng!

533
00:37:15,080 --> 00:37:15,621
Pleng!

534
00:37:15,658 --> 00:37:16,658
Tontharn!

535
00:37:20,020 --> 00:37:21,020
What happened?

536
00:37:23,830 --> 00:37:24,830
Let’s go!

537
00:37:27,287 --> 00:37:29,290
Botpleng, where are you?

538
00:37:29,550 --> 00:37:30,567
Tontharn!

539
00:37:30,610 --> 00:37:31,709
Hang in there, Pleng.

540
00:37:31,750 --> 00:37:33,076
Mom Kan’s coming to get you.

541
00:37:33,112 --> 00:37:34,112
Mom.

542
00:37:38,170 --> 00:37:39,040
Tontharn!

543
00:37:39,076 --> 00:37:40,076
Pleng!

544
00:37:41,790 --> 00:37:42,790
Pleng!

545
00:37:46,500 --> 00:37:47,500
Pleng!

546
00:37:52,470 --> 00:37:53,534
Botpleng!

547
00:37:57,243 --> 00:37:58,243
Botpleng!

548
00:38:15,243 --> 00:38:16,305
What the f*ck?

549
00:38:17,840 --> 00:38:19,061
Botpleng.

550
00:38:19,710 --> 00:38:20,749
Botpleng.

551
00:38:21,270 --> 00:38:22,538
Enough.

552
00:38:23,030 --> 00:38:24,909
Botpleng’s long dead.

553
00:38:25,650 --> 00:38:26,509
Botpleng.

554
00:38:26,552 --> 00:38:27,808
You have to come to terms with it

555
00:38:27,832 --> 00:38:29,403
