556
00:38:31,230 --> 00:38:32,230
Son.

557
00:38:32,890 --> 00:38:34,261
I can remember now!

558
00:38:36,400 --> 00:38:37,400
Tontharn!

559
00:38:40,950 --> 00:38:42,510
I was the one who caused Pleng’s death.

560
00:38:43,498 --> 00:38:44,654
What the f*ck?

561
00:38:45,350 --> 00:38:46,472
I’m not Botpleng.

562
00:38:52,250 --> 00:38:53,418
I’m Tontharn.

563
00:39:01,500 --> 00:39:02,500
Pleng!

564
00:39:02,570 --> 00:39:03,570
Tontharn!

565
00:39:12,360 --> 00:39:13,360
Pleng.

566
00:39:37,060 --> 00:39:38,060
You know what?

567
00:39:38,810 --> 00:39:41,680
I think something is missing in your house.

568
00:39:44,170 --> 00:39:45,389
Ever since you’re here.

569
00:39:45,940 --> 00:39:47,316
I don’t think anything is lacking.

570
00:39:49,680 --> 00:39:50,792
Be serious!

571
00:39:52,830 --> 00:39:53,978
Am I not?

572
00:39:56,560 --> 00:39:57,898
Stop it!

573
00:39:59,469 --> 00:40:00,152
Answer me first.

574
00:40:00,196 --> 00:40:01,196
Hurry up.

575
00:40:02,760 --> 00:40:03,970
Hmm…

576
00:40:06,790 --> 00:40:07,790
I don’t know.

577
00:40:08,596 --> 00:40:10,600
This place has never felt like a home to me.

578
00:40:11,650 --> 00:40:14,378
Ever since Dad, Mom, and Thun died,

579
00:40:14,740 --> 00:40:16,560
Jen also didn’t want this house.

580
00:40:17,160 --> 00:40:18,712
Everything in this house

581
00:40:18,734 --> 00:40:20,710
is all my parents’ pick.

582
00:40:27,600 --> 00:40:28,600
Then…

583
00:40:30,712 --> 00:40:32,710
Do you want it to be our home?

584
00:40:34,710 --> 00:40:36,341
I want to make it our home.

585
00:40:40,960 --> 00:40:41,960
I think.

586
00:40:43,220 --> 00:40:44,880
I like Yai Yaem’s house.

587
00:40:45,592 --> 00:40:47,590
Since you can hear the waterfall all the time.

588
00:40:50,120 --> 00:40:51,570
Shall we build a waterfall?

589
00:40:52,770 --> 00:40:53,770
A waterfall?

590
00:40:54,910 --> 00:40:55,963
Honestly,

591
00:40:56,710 --> 00:40:57,710
I think

592
00:40:58,378 --> 00:41:00,380
it sounds more soothing than a song.

593
00:41:03,430 --> 00:41:04,872
I’m down for whatever you say.

594
00:41:06,870 --> 00:41:07,870
Seriously?

595
00:41:09,220 --> 00:41:10,220
Yeah.

596
00:41:14,260 --> 00:41:15,301
Then…

597
00:41:16,810 --> 00:41:18,210
I’ll be serious too!

598
00:41:18,670 --> 00:41:19,774
Got you!

599
00:41:21,030 --> 00:41:23,185
Got you!

600
00:41:30,650 --> 00:41:32,392
He let me call him my older brother.

601
00:41:32,970 --> 00:41:34,138
He took care of me.

602
00:41:34,630 --> 00:41:36,480
And asked me to be his younger brother.

603
00:41:36,516 --> 00:41:37,716
Hang in there, Pleng.

604
00:41:37,760 --> 00:41:38,960
Mom Kan is coming to help you.

605
00:41:39,170 --> 00:41:39,592
Mom.

606
00:41:39,760 --> 00:41:40,887
Where did Botpleng go?

607
00:41:41,294 --> 00:41:43,290
This Botpleng is not my Botpleng!

608
00:41:43,330 --> 00:41:44,330
That’s not true.

609
00:41:44,570 --> 00:41:45,738
I don’t believe you.

610
00:41:46,140 --> 00:41:47,140
I love you, too.

611
00:41:47,560 --> 00:41:48,560
This you.

612
00:41:48,710 --> 00:41:51,149
It’s always been you.
